<|channel>thought
<channel|># 副簽
(pos:名詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺文件或者合約上面，除咗主要簽署人之外，另外一個簽名嘅人（量詞：個）
eng:co-signatory / second signature
<eg>
yue:呢份合約除咗經理簽咗之外，仲要搵個副簽。 (ni1 fan6 hap6 joek3 ceoi4 zeo2 ging1 lei5 zaang1 zo2 zi1 ngoi6, zung6 jiu3 wan2 go3 fu3 zin1.)
eng:Besides the manager's signature, this contract also requires a co-signatory. [end of text]


